  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Counter Crew (Full time/Part time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Attend to customer orders, perform cashiering and counter operations, assist with food preparation, and support F&B Supervisor tasks at the nearest available outlet based on your residential address.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and take customer orders accurately and efficiently to ensure a positive customer experience</li><li>Operate the cashier system to process payments and manage counter transactions securely</li><li>Prepare food items including desserts, fruit cutting, dim sum, and beverages following training and hygiene standards</li><li>Collaborate with team members to maintain a clean, organized, and safe work environment</li><li>Support additional tasks assigned by the F&B Supervisor to contribute to smooth daily operations</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate genuine interest in the food and beverage industry to engage effectively in daily tasks</li><li>Communicate clearly and build rapport with customers from diverse backgrounds to enhance service quality</li><li>Show punctuality, reliability, and maintain a positive attitude to support team efficiency</li><li>Work independently with minimal supervision by managing time and tasks proactively</li></ul>",
